# Docker 
-->  Software Dev Platform.. 
            -->   to deploy the apps 

-->  Apps are packaged in containers 
            -->    Can run on any OS 

-->  Use Case::  Micro service arch.. 


--> VM's vs  Docker 

VM's
-----------
Apps      |   Apps    | Apps  
GuestOS   |   GuestOS | GuestOS
Hypervisor 
Host OS 
Infrastructure 


Docker 
------

Docker | Docker | Docker | Docker
Docker | Docker | Docker | Docker 
Docker Daemon
Host OS 
Infrastructure 


--------------

Dockerfile 

-------------------------

After spinning up the instance, 
execute the below commands 

sudo su 

yum install docker 

service docker start 

